OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with outbreaks of rain.
OL,7,FRemaining cloudy overnight with
OL,8,Ffurther spells of rain, occasionally
OL,9,Fheavy. Freshening southerly wind along
OL,10,Fthe east coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FQuite cloudy with some rain
OL,13,Fto start. Variable amounts of cloud
OL,14,Fand sunny spells during the day along
OL,15,Fwith scattered slow moving showers,
OL,16,Foccasionally heavy. Becoming drier in
OL,17,Fwest later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
